snippet.title: Two Hundred Ways - Official Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
200 tricky levels to solve in Two Hundred Ways. The goal is to make the ball(s) reach its goal(s). That will be hard because of up to three layers and a lot of traps. To finish the levels, you have some resources but only a limited budget. Think outside the box to have benefits.

Coming soon for PS4 and PS5
